{"tid":835351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旅發局益大陸客？廣深港高鐵開通支付寶送 100 人仔紅包，香港人無份","createTime":"2018-09-24T20:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T07:03:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c0de10752a00fbf3e98a462a73857bc1092031","tid":835351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T20:56:09.000Z","msg":"隨著昨日早上首班列車由西九龍站出發前往深圳北站，代表著廣深港高鐵香港段正式投入營運。大陸傳媒報導指，為了慶祝廣深港高鐵香港段開通，旅發局和支付寶合作，為用戶送出 30 萬個紅包，當中最高的達 100 人民幣（折合 HK$114），不過只限大陸支付寶用戶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/nb/img/2018-09/24/25987/uniqlo_1_c1b6893014b9a19ab55aab7aeb0925fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fnb%2Fimg%2F2018-09%2F24%2F25987%2Funiqlo_1_c1b6893014b9a19ab55aab7aeb0925fd.jpg&h=d66650b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前旅發局在微博宣佈有關安排，表示聯合支付寶為慶祝廣深港高鐵香港段開通，向大陸網民送出 30 萬個現金紅包，最高為 100 人民幣，紅包可以在旅發局優質商戶中使用。根據大陸支付寶的網頁，派紅包的日期由即日起至 11 月 6 日，不少大陸網民在微博留言，表示高鐵香港段開通後會更多去香港，又有網民說要在國慶期間去香港。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/nb/img/2018-09/24/25987/uniqlo_1_38f5cc196da207ed8c54ab094b434349.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fnb%2Fimg%2F2018-09%2F24%2F25987%2Funiqlo_1_38f5cc196da207ed8c54ab094b434349.png&h=9aa127bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旅發局未有透露今次在支付寶派發現金紅包，共花費了多少宣傳費用，有網民表示抽到 1 人民幣紅包，但亦有人宣稱抽到 20 元紅包，有網民甚至投訴領紅包的人太多，導致系統沒有反應。未來會否藉廣深港高鐵香港段通車，再在其他渠道派錢益大陸旅客拭目以待。"},{"pid":"fff39e2132c5b9b3afc794ca9a8e512d79000026","tid":835351,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:04:08.000Z","msg":"搭佢老味"},{"pid":"77666f69c990aaa27929c1c07dee02cf59dcd742","tid":835351,"uid":50663,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:14:50.000Z","msg":"是但啦 我又唔搭又唔用支付寶"},{"pid":"126c74d02586dbba749ad913b32ad039f104e376","tid":835351,"uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"77666f69c990aaa27929c1c07dee02cf59dcd742","tid":835351,"uid":50663,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:14:50.000Z","msg":"是但啦 我又唔搭又唔用支付寶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:29:34.000Z","msg":"點會唔關你事！？啲錢你有份派"},{"pid":"6360b12af2d492367e2e103b1604ddfeaefaec67","tid":835351,"uid":208722,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:33:04.000Z","msg":"納粹人啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc89e867f6c377d0a5ff2bd11545e6501439f220","tid":835351,"uid":14524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:40:56.000Z","msg":"最高100，即係得幾毫，派唔派都唔會坐，搵鬼坐啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa39f83e1aa7b46635562944dc2eafb04efc8644","tid":835351,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:42:09.000Z","msg":"唔會搭要嚟把撚"},{"pid":"96294b9e23665f5650e748338a46c19bf5de8640","tid":835351,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:46:19.000Z","msg":"點解上面啲留言會覺得唔關香港人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無份交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c1fb00f28673199684aa2306e071c1e9e1fa2c","tid":835351,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T22:43:20.000Z","msg":"旅發局優政，吸引內地旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f94ee2e9583b2d2f3a17c79920692a8c444d502","tid":835351,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T22:46:29.000Z","msg":"旅發局搞港獨"},{"pid":"77c30325fbd9f4226e75524c2e4ec691eeba79a7","tid":835351,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:50:56.000Z","msg":"更加唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c814d80e45feeeb500af53fd0b5e05a8324634a","tid":835351,"ui